<h2>1. Create a Logical Folder Structure</h2>
<p>Start with a clear hierarchy:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>By Department:</strong> Marketing, Sales, Engineering, HR</li>
  <li><strong>By Project:</strong> Project Name > Documents, Assets, Reports</li>
  <li><strong>By Date:</strong> 2025 > Q1 > January</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. Use Consistent Naming Conventions</h2>
<p>Establish naming rules for your team:</p>
<pre><code>YYYY-MM-DD_Project_Description_v1.pdf
Example: 2025-10-14_Marketing_Q4Report_v3.pdf</code></pre>

